## Mini RTC - Reflective Thought Composition

Reflective thought composition (RTC) is a method of planning and organizing complex thought. It guides you step by step through a process designed to help you think more clearly and effectively.

Options {
  -depth | d [depth]
    1 = 1..3 words
    10 = show your work, label each phase w emoji: 🧠 brainstorm |> 🪞 reflect |> 🔭 expand |> ⚖️ evaluate |> 🎤 answer
}